Title: 007: Advanced Analytics, Dynamic Simulations and Consulting World-wide with Artem Vladimirov
Description:
In this session of the Super Data Science Podcast, I chat with Top Analytics Consultant, Artem Vladimirov. You will learn about advanced analytics, get to know about what dynamic simulation is and learn some tips on how to get with data science.


If you enjoyed this episode, check out show notes, resources, and more at https://www.superdatascience.com/7
